    "name": "Swordeye",
    "steam_appid": 2321890,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into brutal, skill‑based combat in this hardcore MMO where your skill with your blade is the only thing standing between you and a quick death. Compete to climb an expansive, interconnected, and persistent tower overflowing with monsters, traps, and treasure. Swordeye combines a fast-paced directional combat system that includes ripostes, feints, parries, kicks, and combos with persistent massive multiplayer dungeons, loot, abilities, and a skill tree.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress you will unlock skills and abilities, craft potions, upgrade gear and customize your combat style as you strive to gain power and reach the top of the tower. Each floor of the tower is a unique hand-crafted dungeon crawl with a variety of different enemies, trials, and traps, as well as the ever-present threat of other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/e7921ef8347f1621de2374f420566029.avif?t=1770480612\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Group up with friends or engage as a lone warrior to face off against the dangers of the tower.  Compete to traverse massive interconnected dungeons filled with monsters, bosses, traps, and loot. Can you make it to the top?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/fca9f2f6e653e593814cfde64f5c7cea.poster.avif?t=1770480612\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/fca9f2f6e653e593814cfde64f5c7cea.webm?t=1770480612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/fca9f2f6e653e593814cfde64f5c7cea.mp4?t=1770480612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/b4f955012426262305469dfe25d58f71.avif?t=1770480612\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swordeye's &quot;easy to learn, difficult to master&quot; directional combat system provides a fluid yet brutal combat experience that will keep you coming back day after to day to hone your skills. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/e0a3b8d6f848e5bf67fd8b1b652fe5b2.poster.avif?t=1770480612\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/e0a3b8d6f848e5bf67fd8b1b652fe5b2.webm?t=1770480612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/e0a3b8d6f848e5bf67fd8b1b652fe5b2.mp4?t=1770480612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/77f666d871d4fe281eef3e3808390966.avif?t=1770480612\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slay bosses, find chests, or kill other players within the tower, then find an exit portal to escape with your loot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/c5aa485aa138e0b34650a82809828aa6.poster.avif?t=1770480612\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/c5aa485aa138e0b34650a82809828aa6.webm?t=1770480612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/c5aa485aa138e0b34650a82809828aa6.mp4?t=1770480612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/388c251b43b1125cf133b4c92cbd6681.avif?t=1770480612\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your loot to upgrade your sword and craft new gear. Level up, and unlock powerful new skills and abilities to use against your foes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/8f22717edad9fdc7e318063b8d1d139c.poster.avif?t=1770480612\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/8f22717edad9fdc7e318063b8d1d139c.webm?t=1770480612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/8f22717edad9fdc7e318063b8d1d139c.mp4?t=1770480612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
